<p>I have the following models:</p>  <pre><code>class UserProfile(models.Model):     user = models.OneToOneField(User)  class Property(models.Model):     user = models.ForeignKey(User) </code></pre>  <p>I would like to create a <code>TabularInline</code> displaying every Property connected to a particular <code>UserProfile</code> on its Django admin page. The problem here is, of course, that Property does not have a <code>ForeignKey</code> directly to <code>UserProfile</code>, so I cannot simply write</p>  <pre><code>class PropertyTabularInline(admin.TabularInline):     model = Property  class UserProfileAdmin(admin.ModelAdmin):     inlines = (PropertyTabularInline,) </code></pre>  <p>How can I easily do what I want?</p>